
# ğŸ” Secure User Authentication System (Flask + Argon2)

A minimal yet secure user registration and login system built with Flask, SQLite, and Argon2id password hashing. Designed for educational and real-world use, this project demonstrates best practices in password storage, salting, and authentication workflows.

