## ğŸš€ Features

- âœ… User registration and login with email + password
- ğŸ” Passwords hashed using **Argon2id** (memory-hard, salted)
- ğŸ§‚ Unique salt per password (handled by Argon2)
- ğŸ§Š Optional pepper support for added security
- ğŸ—„ï¸ SQLite database with secure schema
- ğŸ§  Rate-limiting stub to prevent brute-force login attempts
- ğŸ§¼ Clean UI with inline HTML templates
- ğŸ§ª Easy to extend for email verification, password reset, or JWT

